  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937330/extras/ef0dcd45bf41e034243005a2e364a55b.poster.avif?t=1765193557\" width=736 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937330/extras/ef0dcd45bf41e034243005a2e364a55b.webm?t=1765193557\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937330/extras/ef0dcd45bf41e034243005a2e364a55b.mp4?t=1765193557\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Help Us DOSMan, You are our only hope!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937330/extras/ecab2daf4b4c68bd7c2c7b3b0de5203e.avif?t=1765193557\" width=584 height=750 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >FEATURES </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>RETRO SPACE ACTION!</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><i><strong>Break a leg. Theirs.</strong></i></u>: Various Alien races & enemy types, including Interstellar Security guards, aliens, mutants and pods.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><i><strong>Inside Intel:</strong></i></u> Interactive informants that provide you clues and hints.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><i><strong></strong></i></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><i><strong>Future Soldier:</strong></i></u> A plethora of futuristic weapons - from a blaster shotgun to an explosive orb grenade launcher.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><i><strong></strong></i></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><i><strong>EXPLORE PLANETS DOS: </strong></i></u>Staggering levels, including secrets a plenty.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >STORY</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspired by the \"hero\" shooters of the late 90s such as Duke Nukem, Blake Stone, and Wolfenstein 3D, DOSMan: Space Aliens in Space is a retro FPS game where players take on the role of the titular, DOSMan.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Aliens have invaded Planet DOS, and are wreaking havoc upon the population. It’s up to DOSMan and a colorful cast of hilariously incompetent characters to beat them back and restore order to the once-peaceful planet.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game Cover Art by Joe Roman (Chito)</p>",
